{"tid":1631354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌哂你哋香港大人老豆老母","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:33:37.000Z","uid":314384,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b01c3b653594a170a80b3dbca4a9725263c6c30b","tid":1631354,"uid":314384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:20:10.000Z","msg":"今日被捕嘅義士裏面有一個十二歲嘅細路女<br />\n<br />\n你會話 我好嬲 啲狗冇人性 最衰都係個仆街政府<br />\n<br />\n我會話最撚冷血嘅係你哋啲香港人<br />\n<br />\n前一日Po ig講香港人反抗 好嬲 <br />\n<br />\n之後第日就繼續番工<br />\n<br />\n你咁樣同<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推啲細路去死</span></span>有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n<br />\n口裏面講時代革命 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連罷工都唔肯講咩革命姐</span><br />\n<br />\n成日話藍絲活喺平行世界 你哋去完和理非遊行之後都係繼續返工咋 <br />\n<br />\n有一百萬人罷工五日即刻嬴撚咗啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港人 我屌哂你哋老豆老母</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"461a33cecd0f2a5ea6bdbdd3955e7449eea16407","tid":1631354,"uid":314384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:22:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>連罷工都唔肯講咩革命姐</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"9b260acaacd1e4c5b8063ab081ce17395d8b79a9","tid":1631354,"uid":314384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:23:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">連罷工都唔肯講咩革命姐</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9921cc3df82cc09c72fc866a3900dbaa51434c7b","tid":1631354,"uid":314384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:24:09.000Z","msg":"連罷工都唔肯講咩革命姐"},{"pid":"369d53ac21132e9e7451e6b736adbe2190d0bb9a","tid":1631354,"uid":314384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:26:06.000Z","msg":"自己十連推(1/10)"},{"pid":"0c1218ab934e79acc49c9dcf19d11cda9144ac3d","tid":1631354,"uid":314384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:26:16.000Z","msg":"自己十連